document_data.Notable Members:
* [[Belgos Faen Tlabbar]], a [[drow]] myrmidon from the city of [[Nykhandthandar]].<ref>{{Cite organized play/LC/The Jig Is Up|31}}
* [[Gary the Bold]], a myrmidon in [[Ravens Bluff]] that taught a class on martial skills relevant to myrmidons at the city's [[Children’s Vocational Center]].<ref>{{Cite organized play/LC/The Challenge of Children|5}}
* [[Samoth Dier]], the mercenary that replaced [[Gaurundur Thasz]] in the [[Company of the Blue Bear]].
* [[Simmon Thul]], a burly [[Amn]]ian mercenary that served with the same company.
